{"tid":767433,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日終於明白長途車中間無站停,而又劇烈肚痛屎頭突出狂死忍既感覺","createTime":"2018-08-04T13:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T14:44:16.000Z","uid":119688,"like":8,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcfd852f91fbb573b5858632621b29c081d6d06","tid":767433,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:31:58.000Z","msg":"本身收工正常上巴士<br />\n打左鋪手機game<br />\n之後個肚就痛<br />\n仲要係屎急果隻痛 係想瀨出黎果隻<br />\n我坐上層巴士最chok 個肚就好似朗朗下咁 忍到我扯旗加手指腳指夾到實......<br />\n全程巴士去到終點起碼40分鐘<br />\n全程忍到我好辛苦<br />\n成日人喇埋一舊 好似抽筋咁<br />\n架巴士一快少少 d屎就快噴出黎<br />\n經過三十分鐘巴上死忍<br />\n加上返屋企入到廁所果十分鐘<br />\n真係好似返左去戰國時代....<br />\n返到黎條底褲已經有屎跡<br />\n一坐落去馬筒真係十級大解放<br />\n果種感覺真係唔識用文字去形容<br />\n之後慢慢屙住上連登開post分享<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/04/213149_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2F213149_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f6c027af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd768b6d10fd8f64e76edabb5dcf39b299239f54","tid":767433,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:33:15.000Z","msg":"上黎報個平安 而家一身鬆哂"},{"pid":"ea701fee2be26a7aef1638fca3ab8245b6b07aab","tid":767433,"uid":168180,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母講還講唔好post圖</span>"},{"pid":"348867ce0bba6b64fae57f73d3b30556b813ff61","tid":767433,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 椰汁炸豬扒"},{"pid":"c952d500d848089e605806617f428f7bd90b9e12","ti